      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOTTLES OF SHELLS (2) is a former Waterhouse/Bott galloper kicking off for the new yard. Recent impressive trial winner. Has plenty of ability and sure to run well this line-up. NEXT EXIT (9) is back after a break of eight months. At the last run before the layoff she finished fourth over 1150m at Gold Coast Poly. Has ability and is a solid chance. REIGN OF DAME (10) is a four-start maiden who returned last time and finished fourth at Toowoomba over 870m, beaten 0.8 lengths. Will derive great benefit from that outing and deserves consideration. KALIZMA (6) is a three-year-old filly who is having her first run for the Chris Anderson barn. Hasn't raced since finishing eighth at Mornington six months ago. Placed in a recent trial and looks nicely placed. Can return with a bold run. IMZADA (5) is a former Victorian having first run this area so don't underestimate.",
